      "side": 1,
      "message": "At this point, could we just get rid of copy_constant entirely, and call clone() at the call sites? The two in VariableReference are already checking that the argument is a compile-time-constant, so the assert isn\u0027t useful (and Settings values are always constant, but we could add the check there to be more explicit). I think seeing calls to clone() would make it clearer what\u0027s happening, and having the utility function live in VariableReference further obscures the point.",
